1. INTRODUCTION
================
    HARDRIVE is  a  user supported program.  It is not public domain.You
    may use HARDRIVE and give it to your friends,  but you may not  sell
    it  or  use  it  in  business  without obtaining a license.  See the
    section 2 for information about licensing.

    Driver HARDRIVE.SYS permits  to  use  a  little  specially  prepared
    diskettes  as  one DOS disk of summary capacity.  At work the driver
    supervises the reference to appropriate sites of a disk and  at  use
    of  data,  located  on  different  diskettes  to  signals user about
    necessity their replacement,  informing the  number  of  a  required
    diskette  in  a  left-hand  top  corner of a screen and submitting a
    sound signal.


